{
  "stem": "20405.4",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were going to take the-- we was going to-- to take the dead bodies, to put them down there from the elevator, to put them down there, and holding their head, not-- not the heads of the dead bodies to get heat from the cement.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Instead, we could-- we could saw-- the Poland people getting in the bodies, and just to threw it, just like it were like a piece of junk.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Thrown them in.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They did-- they didn't care.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But we were new over there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We didn't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We were afraid that we could believe what was going-- what were happening.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And when the kapos came in with a stick on it and to show us to take them like they were taking the other guys were taken and threw it like a piece of-- of junk on the floor, we started doing the same thing, not because-- not to get beaten.",
      "word_count": 51
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And where there were all this line about 30 people was right on the floor over there, maybe it was 36 people.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It really doesn't matter.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I don't remember exactly how many.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I didn't count it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "A couple a Jewish prisoners again with a gun, they were from France, or maybe those ones, they were not from France.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Anyway, they had in their hands a kind of pliers.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And was taking out all the teeth of the dead bodies.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At that time, everybody used to have golden teeth.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we stayed-- they were taking-- there was take all day the teeth from the dead bodies.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And after that, that we said, Dario and me, taking one by one of them, put them in the what they call them?",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This-- they got them for sick people in their emergencies.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Stretcher.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Stretcher.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
